msgid ""
"Queued messages will be sent after you have manually checked for new mail, "
"&eg; with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Of course, you may also send the queued messages "
"manually via <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send queued "
"messages</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ootel kirjad saadetakse ära pärast seda, kui oled käsitsi uusi kirju "
"kontrollinud, &eg; menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kontrolli posti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Mõistagi "
"võib ootel kirju saata ka käsitsi menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Saada järjekorras ootavad kirjad</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configure.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "On All Mail Checks"
msgstr "Alati uute kirjade kontrollimisel"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:840
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Queued messages will be sent after all checks for new mail, &ie; after "
#| "automatic mail checks as well as after manual mail checks. Of course, you "
#| "can also manually send the queued messages with "
