#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the <guilabel>Date Display</guilabel> section you can choose between "
#| "several date formats. The <guilabel>Localized Format</guilabel> is the "
#| "one you can specify under <guilabel>Country/Region &amp; Language</"
