"regularly. This option lets you specify how often a backup copy is created. "
"You can disable autosaving by selecting \"No autosave\"."
msgstr ""
"Redaktori aknas olevast tekstist saab regulaarselt teha varukoopia. Selle "
"valikuga saab määrata, millise ajavahemiku järel varukoopida tehakse. "
